com.o3dr.services.android.lib.gcs.event

Class GCSEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.o3dr.services.android.lib.gcs.event.GCSEvent

  • public class GCSEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores the list of gcs events (as action), and their extra parameters. The defined events are used in system broadcasts.
